Dialogs.Dialog: Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you like to watch TV？
Hmm？ Not that much.
Which means you usually don't watch TV, huh？
But I often watch movies.
Like, DVDs？
Yeah, and sometimes I like to read books.
I see. I guess that's what I picture you'd do.
Ah, but there's a TV program that I like.
Eh？ Which program？
The late night Western movies program. Sometimes they show very old movies. They're very good.
But that's...
Ah, you'd call it a movie, huh？ Yeah, but for me, I prefer watching movies rather than watching TV.
Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. What is your favorite food？
I love everything, but... If you ask what I like most, it's gonna be cough drops.
...Which means you like candies？
No, not regular candies in general.
So, it has to be cough drops？
Yeah. It has become a habit of mine.
Is your throat weak？
No, that's not the case. I started to like cough drops some time ago, and it's just continued.
You haven't gotten bored of it yet, huh？
Hehe. That's right. Sorry, my answer is just so plain.
(Actually, it's somewhat uncommon...)
Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
Speaking of which, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you have any sports you like？
Eh？ Ah... Why do you ask？
I'm just curious. Are there any？
No. I'm an indoor type by nature.
Do you go to swim in summer, at least？
Eh！？ Ah, hmm... Not much, I think.
You don't go to the sea or the swimming pool？
Not that I don't want to go, but... Don't laugh, okay？
Eh？ I won't laugh.
I... can't swim. Ah, this is embarrassing.
(You don't have to be that embarrassed...)
Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you often listen to music？
No, not quite often. Usually, I listen to movie soundtracks, I think.
Eh？ Soundtracks, huh？
I bought many CDs of my favorite movies' soundtracks. They are very good.
Could it be that you also buy soundtracks for the movies you haven't watched？
For some indie movies, that's pretty much the case. They aren't showed in the theaters here.
Eh？ Even indie movies have soundtracks, too.
Hehe, the movie world is much more profound than you might think. For example...
(I feel like I've just turned on a switch...)
Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
Speaking of which, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you have other hobbies besides watching horror movies？
Horror movies for me... You can say that it's my hobby, but it actually isn't. Hmm.
What's wrong？
Don't tell anyone, okay？
？ Okay, I won't tell.
Well... I collect bags.
Bags？
I collect cough drop bags.
I didn't intend to, but many times, I forgot to throw them away after I finish eating. Now I have them in 4 file folders.
You put them in file folders...？
Sorry. Is that weird？
No, I was just surprised.
It's not like I'm very serious about that. But somehow I just continue collecting them.
It's become your habit, huh？
Yeah, it's more like my habit rather than a hobby. I've been doing it for quite a long time.
Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you like animals？
Yeah, most of them. But I'm not very good with cows and horses.
Cows and horses？
They're usually drooling. And that's... Well...
Then how about your favorite animal？
Hmm... Raccoon dogs, I think.
Raccoon dogs？
Yeah, they look cute with round shape and I feel like I have an affinity with them.
Affinity？
Somehow I can picture myself as a raccoon dog.
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲... as a raccoon dog！？)
Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
I might've already asked you this, but ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what is your dream for your future？
Hehe. "Being someone's bride." ...Is that what you want to hear？
I was expecting a little that you'd say that.
But... Actually, I really want to be a bride.
Is that so？
Is it weird？
No. I'm sure ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ will look great in a wedding dress.
Hehe. What I want to wear isn't a wedding dress, but an apron.
An apron？
Cooking in the kitchen, raising a baby, welcoming a husband from his work... Something like that.
...I can picture that those things suit you.
Hehe. If you wait long enough, you might be able to see it with your own eyes.
Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you have a dream for your future？
Hmm, well...
Do you want to be a horror novel writer？
That's impossible. Being a writer is impossible for me.
Really？ But you read a lot of books.
No. The more I read, the more I realize it.
I don't have the creative urge for writing.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, really？ But you also watch a lot of horror movies.
It's not like I don't want to write, but...
Or do you want to make movies？
No... I've never thought about that.
I see. But that's too bad. I'm very interested in ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s horror movies.
Hehe. If you like to see horror movies this much, how about watching some that are already made？
(Is she going to force me to watch them？)
Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you have any female role models？
Hmm... I've never thought about that...
So you have confidence in yourself, huh？
No, that's not the case. But...
But？
Come on. If you set anyone else as your role model, you'll try to become someone that's not you, right？
I think you're right.
Yeah. For me, if there's something in other people that I don't have, I'll think about how I can achieve that by myself.
That's why you don't have a role model？
Yeah. It's not about a person. If there's something I lack, I'll just try to work my way toward it.
I see...
No. I'm just thinking that I made the right decision to have you as my girlfriend.
Geez... Don't spring stuff on me, okay？
Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Do you have any female role models？
Only restricted to females, huh？
It's different, right？ I just wonder if there's any woman you want to be like.
Hmm... I don't think there's any.
Rather, I don't want to be anyone else but myself. ...Does that sound a little smug？
Come on. There are people who like to say they want to find their true selves, right？
They keep searching for something different or trying to wake up their different selves...
Yeah, I think I've heard about that.
But isn't that very irresponsible to their current selves？
I want to do my best as what I am right now. That might sound complicated, but my role model is myself, I think.
Hmm...？
...What？
I think ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is very cool.
Eh？ Ah... No.
Geez... Idiot.
Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Do you have any female role models？
Why do you ask all of a sudden？
For example... A female horror novel writer or something.
Well... There are people that I admire. However, I don't really have a role model.
I see...
But, why do you ask？ I read from somewhere that people ask this question to find out about others' thought processes, right？
Really？ I didn't have that kind of intention.
Okay, don't worry then. Since it's you, I don't mind being asked this kind of question.
Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what kind of movies do you like？ It must be horror movies, right？
Of course！ But, recent horror movies aren't that good.
Really？
They're using more CGs, but the picture quality is getting worse...
With computer graphics, the picture quality is getting worse？
Yeah. Compared to old movies... I think it's the atmosphere that feels different. Don't you agree？
Well then, you like movies without CGs better？
Yeah, CGs are necessary for some kinds of movies, but for me... I prefer analog.
Analog...？ Somehow I feel like ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ might not be good at using technical stuff.
Ah. Geez！ I'm really concerned about that！
(Bull's eye, huh...？)
Hey.
姉ヶ崎
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. You can read books very fast, right？ How fast are you？
My reading pace？ I can read about 10 books in a month... I think.
So you can finish a book in 3 days？ That's amazing.
I think it's not fast at all. Some people can read 3 books in a day.
You should try. Maybe you can reach that level, too.
That's impossible for me, I think. I also have movies to watch.
I see.
Yeah... And lately, I've been spending time with something else, too.
No, never mind. I was just talking to myself.
